                </div>
                <div class=' text-center justify-center items-center'>
                    <img src="../img/amrit light show.jpg" alt=""
                        class="sm:w-full md:w-[90%] mx-auto h-[600px] rounded-lg" data-aos="fade-right" />
                </div>
                <div class=' px-10 py-10 mt-8 gap-10'>

                    <div class='px-2 text-2xl text-justify' data-aos="fade-left">we specialize in delivering exceptional
                        event management services tailored to meet your unique needs and exceed your
                        expectations. From corporate gatherings to private celebrations, we offer a diverse range of
